ygData.messageBody:
BTW how many actually read the bios when they inspect people? I
personally read the bios when I inspect unless the person really wants me
to drool over an item they are wearing.



My bio says, "if you are reading this, you are too close." I know, not real
friendly, but I just hate having my equipment inspected unless I give
permission. It's sort of feels like somebody going through my purse. Heh.


-Treehugger and Songmaker
